data.description: Discover the joys of suburban living in this delightful Ellenwood residence situated in the sought-after Grant Forest Subdivision. Boasting 2,184 square feet, this 4-bed, 2.5-bath property offers the perfect combination of comfort and style.  Upon entering, a welcoming two-story foyer sets the tone for the rest of the house. The cozy fireplace adds warmth and charm to the home, making it ideal for entertaining or enjoying a quiet evening.  Upstairs, you'll find a convenient laundry room and an inviting master retreat with a generously sized walk-in closet. Hosting gatherings is a breeze with its well-designed floor plan, while a home office offers space for productivity, perfect for those who work remotely and need a dedicated space. The backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities. Additionally, enjoy the added security of the included Ring doorbell and smart locks.
